@startuml
title NewEntryMetadataScreen - Загрузка метаданных для новой записи

actor User as User
participant "NewEntryMetadataScreen" as UI
participant "NewEntryMetadataViewModel" as VM
participant "GetBrandsUseCase /\nGetModelsForBrandAndYearUseCase" as UC
participant "DefaultReferenceDataRepository" as REPO
participant "BrandDao / ModelDao / YearDao" as DAO
participant "AppDatabase" as DB

User -> UI: открывает экран
UI -> VM: onScreenInit()
VM -> UC: invoke()
UC -> REPO: getBrands()
REPO -> DAO: queryAllBrands()
DAO -> DB: SELECT * FROM brands
DB --> DAO: List<BrandEntity>
DAO --> REPO: List<Brand>
REPO --> UC: Result.Success
UC --> VM: updateState(brandsList)
VM --> UI: render EditableDropdownSelector(brands)

User -> UI: выбирает бренд
UI -> VM: onSelectBrand(selected)

User -> UI: выбирает год
UI -> VM: onSelectYear(selected)

VM -> UC: getModels(brandId, yearId)
UC -> REPO: getModels(brandId, yearId)
REPO -> DAO: queryModelsByBrandAndYear(brandId, yearId)
DAO -> DB: SELECT * FROM models\nWHERE brand_id = ? AND year_id = ?
DB --> DAO: List<ModelEntity>
DAO --> REPO: List<Model>
REPO --> UC: Result.Success(modelsList)
UC --> VM: modelsList
VM --> UI: update Models dropdown

User -> UI: нажимает "Далее"
UI -> VM: onSubmitMetadata()
VM -> VM: validate & navigateTo EditEntryDescriptionScreen

@enduml